Welcome to **InSights**, the ultimate Intune management app designed to simplify and enhance your device management experience. With InSights, you can seamlessly manage your Intune tenant and access a wealth of information about your configuration profiles, apps, and policies. This powerful app is built to provide a comprehensive read-only view of your Intune environment with plans for future updates that will include editing and updating capabilities.

